data.description: Rare find on nice Canal into Lake Francis! Properties in this area are hard to come by! Situated on a small private Cul-de-Sac with less than 10 homes, is this spacious home. Home features open main area with large living room with Bay Window, nice dining area, and bright functional Kitchen. This Split Plan home is unique and has essentially two Wings, accessed by steps. The Main Bedroom is roomy and comfortable, with the Bathroom having a walk-in shower, and jetted garden tub. The large Closet/Dressing room has plenty of storage. All Bedrooms have tray ceilings, the front Guest room has a bay window. There is a bright and efficient laundry room just off the hall off the kitchen. The 30' X 11' Screened Porch in back off house provides great views of the canal. Lake Francis is a 500+ acre clean lake for great fishing! Nice Bass are known to be in the canals as well. This lake is great for skiing as well. A beautiful, quiet, clean area between Sebring and Lake Placid, very convenient to everything. Perfect! Schedule your showing today!
